OL,6,
OL,7,GThere have been a few technical
OL,8,Ggremlins with the cameras in BBC News'
OL,9,GStudio B in recent weeks.
OL,11,
OL,12,FWe've perhaps become accustomed to
OL,13,Fseeing the automated cameras in Studio
OL,14,FE going walkies over the years. Such
OL,15,Fincidents are still rare in Studio B.
OL,17,
OL,18,FBut tonight was one of those rare
OL,19,Fexceptions. At the start of the weather
OL,20,Fsegment on the BBC News at Ten, the
OL,21,Fcamera started to swing around.
OL,3,CCamera mishap during the BBC News at
OL,4,CTen
